---
title: Asian Crumbed Banana Blossom Bowl with Garlic Rice, Pickled Onion & Crushed Peanuts
description: Traditionally used in Southeast Asian cooking and with a similar texture to cooked white fish, banana blossom is the perfect
plant-based substitute for a classic Asian-style rice bowl. Packed to the brim with nutritious greens, zingy red onion and crushed peanuts, you'll be glad you trusted us and tried this banging delight.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/asian-crumbed-banana-blossom-bowl-afac9505.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.nz/recipecards/card/asian-crumbed-banana-blossom-bowl-611f1c2ca9447d104214333c-8e7b1cf9.pdf
servings: 2
